@wkk91193 I'm currently doing a quick run of review on all open PRs, and was just wondering if you would still like to get this very old open one merged? If so, could you rebase it, so that we can see if it actually builds on Travis? (FYI when this PR was raised, this project did not have automated CI on Travis set up; but meanwhile it does.)

This one also has review feedback from feedback @avikganguly01 which needs to be taken into account.

Without hearing back within let's say ... 1 month, I would be inclined to just close this (un-merged).

